OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,FBristol City Council has voted to make
OL,7,Fits controversial low-traffic scheme
OL,8,Fpermanent.
OL,10,FThe council introduced its first
OL,11,FLiveable Neighbourhood Scheme in
OL,12,FBarton Hill, parts of St George and
OL,13,FRedfield in September 2024.
OL,15,FIts designed to stop queue-dodging
OL,16,Fcars and encourage people to cycle,
OL,17,Fcatch the bus or walk.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
