CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,FThe council has been trialing the
OL,7,Fscheme and decided to make it
OL,8,Fpermanent at a council meeting on
OL,9,FThursday 9 July, with five votes in
OL,10,Ffavour and four against.
OL,12,FCouncillor Ed Plowden, chair of the
OL,13,Ftransport and connectivity committee,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I'm really pleased that we've
OL,15,Fmade a decision today and we're able
OL,16,Fto get on with it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,F"We're going to continue to listen to
OL,7,Fpeople and we've actually passed an
OL,8,Famendment today which responds
OL,9,Fdirectly to the concerns of the local
OL,10,FMP.
OL,12,F"And we will continue to bring people
OL,13,Fwith us as we continue to develop the
OL,14,Fscheme. It's definitely one of the
OL,15,Fmost controversial things we've had to
OL,16,Fwork on and we're continuing to make
OL,17,Fit more palatable for people."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
