OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,FSue Hughes is someone who relies on a
OL,7,Fcar to get around the city due to her
OL,8,Fdisability. She told ITV News: "There
OL,9,Fwas literally nothing considered on
OL,10,Fthe impact on disabled people.
OL,12,F"Less friends come to visit because
OL,13,Fthey know they're going to sit in a
OL,14,Fqueue. Some taxis and delivery
OL,15,Fcompanies won't even come to the area
OL,16,Fbecause they'll spend so long sat in
OL,17,Fqueues".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
