OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme has proved highly
OL,7,Fcontroversial, with locals blocking
OL,8,Fthe work of council contractors who
OL,9,Farrived after hours to install the new
OL,10,Frestrictions in January 2025.
OL,12,FThe #1.5 million budget for the East
OL,13,FBristol Liveable Neighbourhood (EBLN)
OL,14,Fhas already been doubled and will top
OL,15,F#10 million to fully implement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
