PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,FOne resident told ITV News: "I've
OL,7,Flived in Barton Hill my entire life
OL,8,Ffor 30 years and my parents have been
OL,9,Fhere since 1976. I don't feel it was
OL,10,Fthe right scheme at the right time,
OL,11,Fbearing in mind all the other issues
OL,12,Fthis neighbourhood has had for my
OL,13,Flifetime."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, those who support the
OL,16,Fscheme say they've got their roads
OL,17,Fback and feel safer walking around
OL,18,Fwith less traffic.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
