OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783711192
OL,3,CCouncil narrowly votes to keep
OL,4,Ccontroversial traffic control scheme
OL,6,F"The Greens should ask people before
OL,7,Fdoing things - not say they know best,
OL,8,Fthe people who live here know best,"
OL,9,Fsays resident Sheila Barrett.
OL,11,F"I hope they reconsider and take it
OL,12,Fall out and put it back where it was."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
